{"tid":1287983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港童軍 回歸前後 邊個話童軍唔關政治事？","createTime":"2019-07-05T12:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:58:57.000Z","uid":241293,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb2ab72b737547dd291dc75e942d28eed29ad49","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"有感而家嘅童軍仔已經唔知童軍回歸前後嘅變化<br />\n其實回歸之後香港童軍做咗一系列嘅嘢<span style=\"color: red;\">去殖民地化</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個post係希望而家嘅童軍知道回歸前後對童軍嘅影響，其實所有嘢都關乎政治。當大家仲好慶幸可以用英式童軍步操嗰陣，希望大家好好珍惜，並且好好記低香港最美好嘅年代。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">童軍誓詞</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸前</span><br />\n我願以信譽為誓 竭盡所能<br />\n對神明 對<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>本土</strong></span> 盡責任<br />\n對別人要幫助 對規律必遵行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸後</span><br />\n我願以信譽為誓 竭盡所能<br />\n對神明 對<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國家</strong></span> 盡責任<br />\n對別人要幫助 對規律必遵行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">童軍最高獎章</span><br />\n回歸前後中文名一樣叫做榮譽童軍獎章，不過英文有好大嘅分別。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸前</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8tUmHL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8tUmHL.png&h=bb54303f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nQUEEN SCOUT AWARD<br />\n(註: 英式嘅童軍係用君主作為童軍最高獎章，所以最早期嘅章係叫做&rdquo;京童軍獎章&rdquo; KING SCOUT AWARD (King Edward VI)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸後</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Suttrbt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuttrbt.png&h=15166500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHKSAR SCOUT AWARD (1997-2003別稱沙士 SARS)<br />\nDRAGON SCOUT AWARD (2008-)<span style=\"color: red;\">(龍的傳人嘅意思)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(註: 由於回歸之後香港冇咗君主，所以當時係諗住跟美式嘅傳統，以動物代表童軍最高獎章。而最初草擬嘅係叫做LION SCOUT AWARD，不過最後取消呢個名稱。)<br />\n(例: 美國鷹童軍 Eagle Scout 韓國老虎童軍 Tiger Scout)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">童軍總領袖</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸前</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/43/Chris_Patten_-2008-10-31-_%28cropped%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F43%2FChris_Patten_-2008-10-31-_%2528cropped%2529.jpg&h=5f4fd7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港港督<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸後</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.a1c1.com.hk/images/upload/18/4ca32581e7d074f83d7b38bafee315dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.a1c1.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fupload%2F18%2F4ca32581e7d074f83d7b38bafee315dd.jpg&h=4bda14ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港特首<br />\n(註: 順帶一提，雖然梁振英肯着着童軍制服出現嘅香港總領袖，但係佢身上面嗰兩個勳章都係着禮服先佩戴嘅小型章，所以嚴格來講佢係制服不整)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港童軍章</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸前</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ut5twF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ut5twF.png&h=c3e59e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此章係香港盾徽為本，當年使用嗰陣係要經過政府批准<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">回歸後</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uVC35j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uVC35j.png&h=1e8bb732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然冇咗當年嘅美感，但係唯一嘅德政就係冇用好核特嘅抽氣扇放上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我重申</span>呢個post係希望而家嘅童軍知道回歸前後對童軍嘅影響，其實所有嘢都關乎政治。當大家仲好慶幸可以用英式童軍步操嗰陣，希望大家好好珍惜，並且好好記低香港最美好嘅年代。</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多嘢可以分享，大家有反應我繼續post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d513955efa48a95a67177feb1f0ba31a0da21e7","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">榮譽童軍獎章證書及DofE/AYP</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">回歸前</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5G2uaQ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5G2uaQ8.png&h=bdeb2575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最早期由於香港屬於英國童軍嘅分會<br />\n所以係冇中文版，後來證書加入左中文勉勵詞，內地為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">X X X 君立志為榮譽童軍服務人羣盡忠神明充份表現<br />\n童軍運動崇高之友愛精神謹祝人生旅程愉快事事如意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外簽名嗰個係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">英女王</span></span>。而當年仲有代章制度，考完Queen&rsquo;s嘅童軍會一併有DogE 愛丁堡獎勵計劃金章，而簽名係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">皇夫愛丁堡公爵</span>。所以變相你會有齊晒佢兩個嘅簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.abingdon.org.uk/uploads/school/galleries/22524/img_5367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abingdon.org.uk%2Fuploads%2Fschool%2Fgalleries%2F22524%2Fimg_5367.jpg&h=5939cb8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">回歸後</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ef79Vn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fef79Vn8.png&h=cb5e16e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(1997-2011)<br />\n茲證明ＸＸＸ考獲榮譽童軍獎章 <br />\n(2012-) (變返做勉勵詞，不過加入左<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家</span></span>一詞)<br />\n<br />\nX X X 君立志為榮譽童軍，<br />\n盡忠神明，服務<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家</span></span>社群，充份表現<br />\n童軍運動崇高之友愛和助人精神，<br />\n祝願人生旅程豐盛，生活愉快。<br />\n<br />\n宜家嘅簽名亦都冇咁值錢，改為香港總監簽名<br />\n而DofE回歸之後亦都改為AYP香港青年獎勵計劃，簽名改為香港特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8DMXCN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8DMXCN.png&h=95afe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(網上圖片，蝗二代考完AYP金章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hcs.edu.hk/website/article/article_detail?channel_id=2603&amp;article_id=33483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hcs.edu.hk%2Fwebsite%2Farticle%2Farticle_detail%3Fchannel_id%3D2603%26article_id%3D33483&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=fb04bda6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hcs.edu.hk/website/article/article_detail?channel_id=2603&amp;article_id=33483</a>)"},{"pid":"787812171f53d048b225385e70c1f14ff4bfb55c","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思好多錯字，排版亦都1999<br />\n(唔係好識預啲字嘅大細)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c131397202fbd40ddef34cea8f665abf59066780","tid":1287983,"uid":24875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n步操會唔會有變既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6c5cacab56e3fb56399a828700c7a5ec41393b","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c131397202fbd40ddef34cea8f665abf59066780","tid":1287983,"uid":24875,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n步操會唔會有變既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"真心唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實參考其他國家，轉都係一件好&rdquo;正常&rdquo;嘅事<br />\n例如馬來西亞都係用英式嘅操法，不過用馬拉文嘅口令<br />\n只係希望呢一日遲啲先來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90de0b4964565c5171b11e8eaa78bd2424a29905","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74e9ec70e356a2129f7159e7bca9f390dc82755d","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db5010548d0e58b65e4f7f62317bdf4790991497","tid":1287983,"uid":211021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de531a13b37058e5cad6852fbd0f8485496fdc9a","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee6a48a9b286576c23560ef677856820e4cf4acc","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06e4112045582d6237bee7e300ee8171a3ffc928","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5bb3429caedd970965d9a7c0c49ea5816398e48","tid":1287983,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"咪撚轉操法同口令....<br />\n以前玩童軍最自豪就係上場操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c8b6e2149791ab43c6dc44627ca6540188d564","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5bb3429caedd970965d9a7c0c49ea5816398e48","tid":1287983,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"咪撚轉操法同口令....<br />\n以前玩童軍最自豪就係上場操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:24:25.000Z","msg":"好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女童軍都..."},{"pid":"d119ccaff6b7bbb20cbe264a951db53a88851900","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:15:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e98b30ed2d4090d3fc67c733754ecca4f6bab6f8","tid":1287983,"uid":267152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:25:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63fa81e0ad8170e8cb4bc6ddd720df88db33693b","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3fd6807a081492c5ed455072c484cd0fcd4b327d","tid":1287983,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"仲會有人玩UG咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eebda3ab93c6ac27f2fa7d804269ad6967b79bc","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fd6807a081492c5ed455072c484cd0fcd4b327d","tid":1287983,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"仲會有人玩UG咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:23:27.000Z","msg":"其實香港青少年玩UG嘅佔比算高<br />\n所以正苦先想向UG落手"},{"pid":"d7ed9ea9a2ab76d4282e1f18ee6d4c1c164aa9b9","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a2cb959d1be3d9706c9208708bd75fe278f51bd","tid":1287983,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4308528d8a1721f1135a4b1961645d288f3d2b9","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53201b22f38a39234af6c807ed2843f3b12f87b7","tid":1287983,"uid":26332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"一定要保留英式步操，英式command，英式步操樂隊同風笛隊<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母早排話可能轉中式步操，九唔搭八痴撚線"},{"pid":"872b7efb51d08eefc966496c088d02841cd39028","tid":1287983,"uid":228972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n<br />\n罰抄一百次"},{"pid":"94d910ec239c316d50a114309b201ebd786a4554","tid":1287983,"uid":261553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b7e603cb731bb231cf5715d63f82aa47abd3f37","tid":1287983,"uid":241293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"872b7efb51d08eefc966496c088d02841cd39028","tid":1287983,"uid":228972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n主權移交<br />\n<br />\n罰抄一百次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"對唔住大佬"}]}